snippet.title: Krosmaga – Trailer!
snippet.description:
The Krosmaga beta start on tuesday, october 11th! Iop, Cra, Ecaflip, Sacrier, Sram, Eniripsa: embody the god or goddess you've always dreamed of becoming, and meet legendary heroes such as Yugo, Joris, Percedal, Kerub, or even Goultard. 
Krosmaga is an online collectable card game which lets you embody a god and clash with others. Never before have you been so close to the world of the gods! 
Stop pretending to be a god: become one! 

For more info: 
http://www.krosmaga.com/en
